choices.text: being immoral. They believe that women should undergo pregnancy. In a statement made by President Evo Morales, he said that men bear no responsibility of a ‘failed’ contraception. Resorting to abortion too is not an option for women in this country, and those who encourage the idea of abortion are subject to severe punishment. In fact, penalty highest for anyone caught administering the procedure, resulting in a death penalty. However, if the mother is in an improper state of health and her baby dies as a result of this, one is not subjected to any prison sentence. However if in a stillbirth or abortion happens resulting in a pregnancy loss, the mother and those who helped her in this occasion are subject to imprisonment. Those women who cannot qualify for this, are liable to receive a five-year prison sentence.
